text.section:
On or before December 1 each year, the Commission shall report to the Governor and, in accordance with § 2-1246 of the State Government Article, the General Assembly, regarding:
The number of claims made against each guaranty fund established under this section;
The type, size, and program of the institutions against which the claims are made;
The number of claims that are approved and the associated payouts from the funds; and
The number of claims that are denied.
